This icon represents the location of any damage to your car. If the icon is displayed, it indicates that your car has been damaged in that particular location. For example, if the icon is located at the top left of the screen, it means that your car has been damaged in the top left area.

This icon represents the location of any protected or armored parts of your car. If the shield icon is displayed, it indicates that your car does not have any damage in that particular location. For example, if the shield icon is located at the top left of the screen, it means that the top left area of your car is protected or armored and does not have any damage.
